{"tid":1873162,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中聯辦：香港各界向中國捐款10億元人民幣支援抗疫","createTime":"2020-02-10T13:08:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T14:40:51.000Z","uid":20933,"like":4,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"f119014cd5bdf5e48e82bff063f62b69944a37e3","tid":1873162,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T13:08:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1507774_2_20200210205209.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1507774_2_20200210205209.jpg&h=550ca979&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中聯辦表示，香港社會各界因應疫情，已經通過中聯辦和其他各種渠道，向内地捐款累計折合人民幣超過10億元，一些社團和機構則從海外採購口罩、防護服等防疫物資和醫療設備，送往内地抗疫一線。<br />\n<br />\n中聯辦在網站列出部分捐款的單位和人士，第一個被點名是李嘉誠基金會，基金會通過中聯辦賑災專戶，捐款1億元港幣用作武漢防疫抗疫工作；香港福建社團聯會則捐款300萬元港幣，中聯辦已經與中國紅十字會聯絡轉交善款，由會方根據疫情需要分配及監督使用。<br />\n<br />\n人大代表、政協委員方面，許家印捐款3億元人民幣，呂耀東則以嘉華集團名義捐款2000萬元港幣。<br />\n<br />\n中聯辦表示，當前正處於抗疫關鍵時期，將繼續及時轉達香港社會各界，對内地疫情防控工作的關心支持，全力支持特區政府和社會各界採取有效措施，加強疫情防控和病患救治工作。"},{"pid":"954f62788223d0e4765e53be420fe17174a66f24","tid":1873162,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T13:08:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507774-20200210.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507774-20200210.htm&d=u5wkwi0qRaq%2FdbVqa5yG4RR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=ddb89510\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507774-20200210.htm&h=361f62bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507774-20200210.htm</a>"},{"pid":"80085448f56e8b9351fc9d25d38694daa568be23","tid":1873162,"uid":21545,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T13:09:03.000Z","msg":"勒索<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"275ba1f6b5d4a9d0274b854c357cd949de3d7d85","tid":1873162,"uid":31017,"like":3,